Found it......

We've set this "hidden_modules" thing that HubSpot provides in order to hide default modules(<https://developers.HubSpot.com/docs/cms/building-blocks/themes/hide-modules-and-sections#hide-default-modules-in-a-theme|source>) from the GUI.

But it's pretty clear that hiding it from the hs GUI is not the only thing it does - it will hide it from the internal blog post  as well &gt;_&gt;
